{"tid":153388,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"君如反擊連登仔","createTime":"2017-03-12T14:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T14:35:11.000Z","uid":86117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b34d7a504facfe3ab5aa093c83eca617c74a8286","tid":153388,"uid":86117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"【21連勝】Rex半年後對日本拳王河野公平<br />\n<br />\n近幾年講完又講，曹星如挑戰世界冠軍寶座的對手，是日本拳王河野公平，可惜這場決戰一直約唔成，而河野公平亦失去世界冠軍金腰帶。等到依家，這場遲來的決戰終於打得成，經理人劉志遠透露，今年9月或10月，會安排曹星如與河野公平對戰，地點待定，或者在澳門聯同鄒市明一起舉辦，如果澳門搞唔成就在香港搞，日內劉志遠將飛赴日本，與河野的經理人商討比賽條件。<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170312/bkn-20170312020323874-0312_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170312%2Fbkn-20170312020323874-0312_00882_001.html&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=677456ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170312/bkn-20170312020323874-0312_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">人地輸左之後先打把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"d5f45802ae4621896e38d19184505b3ce09c6275","tid":153388,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"我信佢今次打"},{"pid":"83fe9f6ac0bd1a36ea732690e80af2048e6a848d","tid":153388,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"咁井上呢？"},{"pid":"eb40c06ed232e7c5e266033742ef8ab6c2f8b3b6","tid":153388,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"打井上尚彌未"},{"pid":"0e7eb5c767f320f998f1eab8e00d032ba8066505","tid":153388,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"